bicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1017582, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O All-generous! O All-generous! O All-generous! O All-great! O All-great! O All-great! O Greater than all great ones! O Hearer of prayers! O Unaffected by nights and days! (Please) send blessings upon Muhammad and his Household and have mercy on my feebleness, neediness, destitution, and poverty, because You know them better than I do and You know my need better than I do. O He Who had mercy upon Jacob, the old man, when He returned Joseph, the delight of his eyes, to him! O He Who had mercy upon Job after a long time of tribulation! O He Who had mercy upon Muhammad, Allah’s peace and blessings be upon him, Who gave shelter to him against orphanhood, Who gave him victory against the tyrants and despots of Quraysh and Who gave him control over them! O Bringer of aid! O Bringer of aid! O Bringer of aid!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay kareem, ay kareem, ay kareem, ay azeem, ay azeem, ay azeem, ay sab azmat waalo’n se azeem-tar, ay dua ko soonne waale, ay jis par raat-din ke badal-ne ka asar nahi hota, rehmat naazil farma Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur Aale Muhammad (a.s) par, meri kamzoori, na-daari, tangi aur aajezi par keh Tu unko mujh se ziyadah jaanta hai aur meri haajat se waaqif hai, ay jisne boodhe (senior) Yaqoob (a.s) par rahem kiya jab unke noor'e nazar Yoosuf (a.s) ko un se milwa diya, ay woh jis ne lambi museebat ke baad Ayyoob (a.s) par rehmat farmaya, ay Woh jisne Muhammad (s.a.w.a) par rahem farmaya aur yateemi mein unko panah di, Quresh ke jaabir o zaalim raeeso’n ke muqaable unko fatah di aur hukumat ataa ki, ay faryaad-ras, ay faryaad-ras, ay faryaad-ras.", "Urdu": "اے کر یم،اے کریم، اے کریم، اے عظیم، اے عظیم،اے عظیم، اے سب عظمت والوں سے عظیم تر، اے دعا کو سننے والے، اے وہ جس پر رات دن کے بدلنے کا اثر نہیں ہوتا رحمت فرما محمدؐ پر اور آلؑ محمد ؐ پر رحم کر میری کمزوری ناداری تنگی اور عاجزی پر کہ تو ان کو مجھ سے زیادہ جانتا ہےاور تو میری حاجت سے واقف ہے اے جس نے بوڑھے یعقوبؑ پر رحم کیا جب ان کے نورِ نظریوسف ؑ کو ان سے ملوادیا، اے وہ جس نے لمبی مصیبت کے بعد ایوبؑ پر رحم فرمایا، اے وہ جس نے محمدؐ پر رحم فرمایا اور یتیمی میں ان کو پناہ دی قریش کے جابر وظالم رئیسوں کے مقابل ان کو فتح دی اور حکومت عطا کی، اے فریاد رس، اے فریاد رس اے فریاد رس۔", "RArabic": "YAA KAREEMO YAA KAREEMO YAA KAREEMO, YAA A’ZEEMO YAA A’ZEEMO YAA A,ZEEMO, YAA A’ZAMA MIN KULLE A’ZEEME, YAA SAMEE-A’D DUWAA’E, YAA MAN LAA TAGHIY-YERO-HUL LAYAA-LEE WAL-AYYAA-MO, SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE-HI, WAR-HAM ZA’FEE WA FAQREE WA FAA-QATEE WA MAS-KANA-TEE, FA-INNA-KA A’LAMO BEHAA MINNEE, WA ANTA A’LAMO BE-HAA-JATEE, YAA MAN RAHE-MASH SHAI-KHA YA’QOO-BA HEENA RADDA A’LAIY-HE YOOSUFA QUR-RATA A’IY-NEHI, YAA MAN RAHEMA AIYYOOBA BA’DA TOOLE BALAA'e HI, YAA MAN RAHEMA MOHAMMADIN SALLAL-LAAHO A’LAIY-HE WA AALE-HI WA MENAL YUTME AA-WAA-HU, WA NASARA-HU A’LAA JA-BAABE-RATE QURAB-SHIN WA TAWAA-GHEETE-HAA, WA AM-KANA-HU MIN-HUM, YAA MOGHEE-SO YAA MOGHEE-SO YAA MOGHEE-SO.", "ArabicText1": "يَا كَرِيْمُ يَا كَرِيْمُ يَا كَرِيْمُ، يَا عَظِيْمُ يَا عَظِيْمُ يَا عَظِيْمُ، يَا اَعْظَمَ مِنْ كُلِّ عَظِيْمٍ، يَا سَمِيْعَ الدُّعَاۗءِ، يَا مَنْ لَا تُغَيِّرُهُ اللَّيَالِيْ وَالْاَيَّامُ، صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِهٖ، وَارْحَمْ ضَعْفِيْ وَفَقْرِيْ وَفَاقَتِيْ وَمَسْكَنَتِيْ، فَاِنَّكَ اَعْلَمُ بِهَا مِنِّيْ، وَاَنْتَ اَعْلَمُ بِحَاجَتِيْ، يَا مَنْ رَحِمَ الشَّيْخَ يَعْقُوْبَ حِيْنَ رَدَّ عَلَيْهِ يُوْسُفَ قُرَّةَ عَيْنِهٖ، يَا مَنْ رَحِمَ اَيُّوْبَ بَعْدَ طُوْلِ بَلَائِهٖ، يَا مَنْ رَحِمَ مُحَمَّدًا صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَآلِهٖ وَمِنَ الْيُتْمِ آوَاهٗ، وَنَصَرَهٗ عَلٰى جَبَابِرَةِ قُرَيْشٍ وَطَوَاغِيْتِهَا، وَاَمْكَنَهٗ مِنْهُمْ، يَا مُغِيْثُ يَا مُغِيْثُ يَا مُغِيْثُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "Arab